NFlick 0.4 (22 Feb 2007)
========================

 * Pressing "escape" key while viewing a photo will return to list
 * Worker dialogs have now proper transiency so they don't block whole device
 * Other dialogs have now proper transiency too
 * Fixing the bad-paging bug for good
 * Adding hw-keys navigation to fullscreen view

NFlick 0.3 (25 Nov 2006)
========================

 * Slightly "hildonizing" the UI
 * Show the photos that don't belong to any set
 * An informational dialog about the cache stats
 * A possibility to clear the cache
 * A possibility to reset (remove) all the private data stored
 * A possibility to disable the cache
 * Fixed bug that caused wrong paging to be set in photolist view
 * Use maemo-launcher for faster startup

NFlick 0.2 (09 Jul 2006)
========================

 * A clickable http link on the frontpage (token)
 * Paged user interface (15 thumbs per page)
 * Auto-rotate photos
 * Show photos fullscreen against a black background
 * Downloaded thumbnails are cached to the device
 * Fixed all bugs & all memory leaks
 * User-interface tweaks
 * Use new, recommended gconf paths for settings

NFlick 0.1 (25 Jun 2006)
========================

 * Initial release

